svg.title: Present weather reported from a manned weather station: Lightning visible, no thunder heard
svg.desc: WMO international weather symbol: No precipitation at the station at the time of observation: No precipitation, fog, ice fog, duststorm, sandstorm, drifting or blowing snow at the station* at the time of observation or during the preceding hour. *The expression “at the station” refers to a land station or a ship: Present weather reported from a manned weather station: Lightning visible, no thunder heard
